1. The user opens the list of historical torrents that shows him the information:
the name of seeding file or directory, the size of torrent data, the time the torrent was added to the list of downloading torrents, 
the time the torrent was added to the list of seeding torrents, the time the torrent was removed from the list of seeding torrents,
the reason why the torrent was removed from the seeding list, the size of downloaded data, the size of seeded data.